title: Backlash Fails To Deter Protesters In Hong Kong's Mongkok Camp
teaser: Armed with a court injunction, city court bailiffs could move to clear part of the Mongkok camp this week. Protesters seem unfazed. They've seen it all, including having dead rodents dropped on them.
